<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> Laqueuer, Walter." Comparative Study of Fascism" by Juan J. Linz. Fascism, A Reader's Guide: Analyses, interpretations, Bibliography. Berkeley and Los Angeles: University of California Press, 1976. p. 15. "Fascism is above all a nationalist movement and therefore wherever the nation and the state are strongly identified."</li>
