<li id="cite_note-Shillony-281">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Shillony_281-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Shillony_281-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFShillony1981">Shillony, Ben-Ami (1981). <i><a href="http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=PN1VOByJjE8C&amp;pg=PA23&amp;vq=young+men's+corps&amp;dq=young+mens+corps+japan&amp;as_brr=3&amp;client=firefox-a&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;sig=uRB38jY0CBEbSE-TfcsPhEuo-QM#PPA23,M1" class="external text" title="http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=PN1VOByJjE8C&amp;pg=PA23&amp;vq=young+men's+corps&amp;dq=young+mens+corps+japan&amp;as_brr=3&amp;client=firefox-a&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;sig=uRB38jY0CBEbSE-TfcsPhEuo-QM#PPA23,M1" rel="nofollow">Politics and Culture in Wartime Japan</a></i>. Oxford University Press. pp.&#160;23–33, 71–75. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0198202601" class="internal">ISBN 0198202601</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=PN1VOByJjE8C&amp;pg=PA23&amp;vq=young+men's+corps&amp;dq=young+mens+corps+japan&amp;as_brr=3&amp;client=firefox-a&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;sig=uRB38jY0CBEbSE-TfcsPhEuo-QM#PPA23,M1" class="external free" title="http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=PN1VOByJjE8C&amp;pg=PA23&amp;vq=young+men's+corps&amp;dq=young+mens+corps+japan&amp;as_brr=3&amp;client=firefox-a&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;sig=uRB38jY0CBEbSE-TfcsPhEuo-QM#PPA23,M1" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=PN1VOByJjE8C&amp;pg=PA23&amp;vq=young+men's+corps&amp;dq=young+mens+corps+japan&amp;as_brr=3&amp;client=firefox-a&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;sig=uRB38jY0CBEbSE-TfcsPhEuo-QM#PPA23,M1</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Politics+and+Culture+in+Wartime+Japan&amp;rft.aulast=Shillony&amp;rft.aufirst=Ben-Ami&amp;rft.au=Shillony%2C+Ben-Ami&amp;rft.date=1981&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B